name: Violin on a mushroom trip wearing a du rag 001
description:
1/4 series: violin, spraypaint, acrylic pour, gold chains, photography, digital manipulation
______

Painted violin wearing du-rag, on a non directional quest to abandon identity, takes mushrooms and they have just started to hit. 

*******
Violin represents artist, Jasminfire, who experienced a love-hate relationship with the instrument. The colors and chains represent an identity she created around it as a defense mechanism for dealing with rejection and difficulty connecting with others outside of a music space.
